description:
This a guide to modifying your 360 drive to play backup games. Every thing u need is included. 

Simply boot using slax to force your drive into modeB, then use 360 firmware toolbox to modify and flash your drive, Even the nasty v78\&amp;#039;s. 

(no bricked drives due to crossed wire trick or bad flashing ) 

Hope this helps ppl who cant use mtkflash and similar programs due to chipset incompatibility


